abstract: MSNBC’s ratings showed increases in the 8 and 9 p.m. hours on the network’s first night without its previous leading man, Keith Olbermann.
snippet: MSNBC’s ratings showed increases in the 8 and 9 p.m. hours on the network’s first night without its previous leading man, Keith Olbermann.
lead_paragraph: MSNBC received some gratifying ratings news from the first night of its new prime-time lineup as it showed increases in the 8 p.m. and 9 p.m. hours, even in the absence of its previous leading man, Keith Olbermann.

headline.main: MSNBC Ratings Rise on First Night Without Olbermann
